+ Effective immediately, you are appointed as the Unit Equal Opportunity Leader
  for the 1st Training Battalion in accordance with AR 600-20.

+ The authority for this appointment is AR 600-20, chapter 6. Your duties
  include the following:

  + Advise the commander on the unit equal opportunity climate.
  + Conduct training and assist with complaint processing.
  + Maintain the unit equal opportunity continuity file.

+ This appointment will remain in effect until you are reassigned, relieved, or
  the appointment is otherwise rescinded in writing.

+ The point of contact for this memorandum is the undersigned.
